	<abstract>
		<para>
			 Clustered systems provide reliability, scalability, and availability to critical production services. Using a &RH; Cluster, you can create high-availability clusters for file sharing, Web servers, and more. This document describes the configuration and management of &RH; cluster systems. It does not include information about &RH; Linux Virtual Servers (LVS). Information about installing and configuring LVS is in a separate document. 
		</para>
